<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.5.6">
<l>kēvala maṉṟuṉ vayiṟu vayiṟṟukku</l>
<l>nāṉava lappam taruvaṉ karuviḷaip</l>
<l>pūvalar nīḷmuṭi nantaṉṟaṉ pōrēṟē</l>
<l>kōvala ṉēkoṭṭāy cappāṇi</l>
<l rend="indent">kuṭamāṭī koṭṭāy cappāṇi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Your stomach is not ordinary; for [that] stomach,</l>
<l>I will give [you] rice flakes and pancakes, Nanda’s battle bull</l>
<l>With blue pea blossoms on a high crown.</l>
<l>Herder, clap your hands;</l>
<l rend="indent">pot dancer, clap your hands!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
